description: Demolition of an existing Almshouse complex and erection of 30 residential units (Use Class C3) comprising 20 no. 1-bed almshouse units, 2 no. 2-bed almshouse units and 8 no. 1-bed units for persons of state pensionable age (of which 23 no. units built to M4(2) standard with M4(3) bathrooms & 7 no. built to full M4(3) standard), with office/meeting room, residents' cafe/social room, ancillary buildings and associated parking and landscaping.
